				<p sameAs="summary">The author tells word by word what an enemy of King Dom Miguel was heard saying publicly against him.</p>
				<p sameAs="settingDesc"> Francisco José Rodrigues was anonymously accused of speaking against the King Dom Migueland his Royal Family in a liquor house.</p>
